text: Holladay is an unincorporated community and census-designated place in Benton and Decatur counties in the U.S. state of Tennessee. Holladay is located along Tennessee State Route 192 which is southwest of Camden. Holladay has a post office with ZIP code 38341. The post office opened on February 23, 1887. ==References== Category:Benton County, Tennessee Category:Census-designated places in Tennessee Category:Unincorporated communities in Tennessee
